<body>
	
<header>
	See if you can remember some things about the speaking section of the IELTS exam.Which of the following statements are true and which are false?
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/TT_SP_003.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <br/>
  <ol id="questionList">
    <br/>
    <li id="q1">The examiner asks all candidates the same questions. <br/></li>
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0f157a">
      <b>
        <a id="a1">True</a>
        <tab/>
        <a id="a2">False</a>
      </b>
    </font>
    <br/>
    <li id="q2">The candidate has to state his or her full name. <a id="a3">True</a><tab/><a id="a4">False</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q3">All three parts of the test are connected to each other. <a id="a5">True</a><tab/><a id="a6">False</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q4">The candidate talks on his or her own about a topic of his choice. <a id="a7">True</a><tab/><a id="a8">False</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q5">The examiner introduces herself to the candidate. <a id="a9">True</a><tab/><a id="a10">False</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q6">The candidate has to produce identification. <a id="a11">True</a><tab/><a id="a12">False</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q7">The candidate has a turn to ask questions. <a id="a13">True</a><tab/><a id="a14">False</a><br/></li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section id="fb1">
  <p align="left">There are several different exam packs examiners can use and each has a variety of questions to choose from.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p align="left">Your name is needed for identification.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p align="left">Only Parts 2 and 3 are connected.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p align="left">The examiner will give you the topic to talk about.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p align="left">Examiners will introduce themselves.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb6">
  <p align="left">Without identification you will not be allowed to take the exam.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb7">
  <p align="left">The candidate can ask for a question to be repeated or clarified but nothing else.</p>
</section>

